{"tid":1813333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為保障公眾安全，醫院應申請禁制令禁止疑似武漢肺炎人士出院，直至有化驗結果!!","createTime":"2020-01-06T08:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T08:07:34.000Z","uid":344174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"080b9fe3c07d113ba0c4a47b24faf7d39ea6fd6c","tid":1813333,"uid":344174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T08:01:56.000Z","msg":"傳有肺炎徵狀內地女子　拒隔離自行出院　報住沙田帝都酒店<br />\n<br />\n武漢不明肺炎疫情擴大，至今本港累計有16宗懷疑個案。本港有公立醫院醫護人員向《立場新聞》透露，其中一懷疑個案、一名內地女子1月初曾由內地出發到武漢，前日抵港，昨日出現發燒等症狀決定往律敦治醫院求醫。醫院安排病人入住隔離病房，X光顯示肺部有陰影，懷疑患有肺炎，因此向衛生防護中心通報。惟女病人其後表示要返回沙田帝都酒店照顧女兒，昨晚要求自行承擔風險出院。<br />\n醫護人員稱，由於衛生防護中心表示無權對該名女病人發隔離令，因此無權要求病人留院，但該名女病人出院時未有病毒化驗結果。<br />\n根據香港法例第599A章《預防及控制疾病條例》第25條，衞生署署長為防止任何指明傳染病蔓延，有權發出隔離令；但傳染病只包括7種，包括沙士、中東呼吸合症、新型甲型流感、廣泛耐藥肺癆、鼠疫、天花及病毒性出血熱。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據法例，若相信某人患指明傳染病，可禁止該人離開香港。<br />\n醫管局昨日公布新個案當中，包括一名 45 歲女子入住灣仔律敦治醫院。醫管局消息人士表示，曾接獲一名45歲女子往律敦治醫院求醫，是昨日其中一名新通報的個案，但正了解病人是否已經出院。醫管局指，稍後將有回覆。《立場新聞》記者下午向衛生署查詢事件，暫待回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9C%89%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E5%BE%B5%E7%8B%80-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%8B%92%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%8C%E5%87%BA%E9%99%A2-%E5%A0%B1%E4%BD%8F%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%B8%9D%E9%83%BD%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E5%25BE%25B5%25E7%258B%2580-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%258B%2592%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%2587%25BA%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E4%25BD%258F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%25B8%259D%25E9%2583%25BD%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25BA%2597%2F&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDR%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=7ac0ab0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E5%25BE%25B5%25E7%258B%2580-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%258B%2592%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%2587%25BA%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E4%25BD%258F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%25B8%259D%25E9%2583%25BD%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25BA%2597%2F&h=ad0b6a4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9C%89%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E5%BE%B5%E7%8B%80-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%8B%92%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%8C%E5%87%BA%E9%99%A2-%E5%A0%B1%E4%BD%8F%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%B8%9D%E9%83%BD%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97/</a>"},{"pid":"b6b9a128ab22999b0a138c590a613b9de21d8d2a","tid":1813333,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T08:02:32.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0065d1665a2eedf653ebedbb9b354f47580c73e7","tid":1813333,"uid":330715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T08:03:00.000Z","msg":"Push ar"},{"pid":"ceb322919e6f014a372ff8a220f06b35653e4dbb","tid":1813333,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T08:03:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e5d487cbdda537a1d9fee72792ce0e41d9e33b4","tid":1813333,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T08:07:34.000Z","msg":"嚴重傷害我國人民感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n------------<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港獨立 唯一出路</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新症正名：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large